  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The is study will examine whether variation in clinical bleeding frequency and severity among
      boys with severe Hemophilia A (Factor VIII deficiency) is associated with variations in
      laboratory measurements of platelet activity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
